ti" title="Koliti – Albanian" lang="sq" hreflang="sq">Shqip</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-simple"><a href="//simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colitis" title="Colitis – Simple English" lang="simple" hreflang="simple">Simple English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sk"><a href="//sk.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kolit%C3%ADda" title="Kolitída – Slovak" lang="sk" hreflang="sk">Slovenčina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fi"><a href="//fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koliitti" title="Koliitti – Finnish" lang="fi" hreflang="fi">Suomi</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sv"><a href="//sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kolit" title="Kolit – Swedish" lang="sv" hreflang="sv">Svenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ta"><a href="//ta.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%86%E0%AE%B0%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%99%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%95%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%9F%E0%AE%B2%E0%AF%8D_%E0%AE%85%E0%AE%B4%E0%AE%B1%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%9A%E0%AE%BF" title="பெருங்குடல் அழற்சி – Tamil" lang="ta" hreflang="ta">தமிழ்</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tr"><a href="//tr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kolit" title="Kolit – Turkish" lang="tr" hreflang="tr">Türkçe</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk"><a href="//uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%96%D1%82" title="Коліт – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B5%90%E8%85%B8%E7%82%8E" title="結腸炎 – Chinese" lang="zh" hreflang="zh">中文</a></li><li class="uls-p-lang-dummy"><a href="#"></a></li>					</ul>
